Introduction

Fuko is a Japanese trainee under WAKEONE.

She mostly gained recognition for her participation on Mnet's survivals shows Girls Planet 999 in 2021, and I-LAND2: N/a in 2024. Unfortunately, Fuko was eliminated in both shows, making her unable to debut.
